OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome early brightness across
OL,6,Fthe south, otherwise cloudy with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,8,Fpersistent across western parts. The
OL,9,Frain turns more showery later with a
OL,10,Frisk of thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,14,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,15,FMainly dry and bright Monday with
OL,16,Fsunny spells, but cloudier Tuesday
OL,17,Fwith rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
